		</div>
		<div id="home_main_content_right">
			
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
<div id="home_sub_content_wrapper">
	<div id="home_sub_content">
		<div class="home_sub_content_column">
			<div class="label">Collect Data Anywhere</div>
			<div class="content">
				Create a free account today and get access to pricing data for thousands of products at your fingertips.
				Setup agents to automatically extract and save data on a schedule. 
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="home_sub_content_column">
			<div class="label">Get Daily Pricing Trends</div>
			<div class="content">
				Get the latest trends for product pricing to help you make the right decisions and respond to changes
				in time. Analyze market movements for new openings.
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="home_sub_content_column">
			<div class="label">Increase Online Presence</div>
			<div class="content">
				Use the data collected via the simple dashboard UI to generate new content and keep your application fresh. More data
				means more content. More content means better indexing and increased traffic. 
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
